---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — ajscanlan.dev" description="Working notebook — engineering, writing, and the space between.">
    <div class="layout-home pt-16 pb-20">

        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-mono text-2xs uppercase tracking-eyebrow text-ink-400 mb-4">
            <span class="size-1.5 rounded-full bg-green shrink-0"></span>
            Dublin, Ireland · Remote
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink-900 mt-0 mb-4">Alexander Scanlan</h1>

        <p class="text-base text-ink-600 max-w-prose-narrow mt-0 mb-8">
            Frontend developer with 12 years of experience across native iOS and Android development. Looking to deepen my understanding of backend and infrastructure - specifically edge AI, distributed systems, and decentralised networks. Looking for an excuse to learn Rust.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-[140px_1fr] gap-x-10 gap-y-0 border-t border-ink-100 max-[640px]:grid-cols-1">
            <span class="font-mono text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-eyebrow text-ink-400 py-4 border-b border-ink-100 max-[640px]:pb-1 max-[640px]:border-b-0">Currently</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-ink-700 py-4 border-b border-ink-100">Looking to expand my skills and find a project that matters.</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-eyebrow text-ink-400 py-4 border-b border-ink-100 max-[640px]:pb-1 max-[640px]:border-b-0">Background</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-ink-700 py-4 border-b border-ink-100">Began software development with Android and Java. Pivoted to iOS with Objective-C and UIKit, before quickly adopting Swift and SwiftUI. Spent several years building and shipping native apps across a wide range of industries, team-sizes, and codebases. I care about UX and quality, and I believe that good code can be felt by the user</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-eyebrow text-ink-400 py-4 border-b border-ink-100 max-[640px]:pb-1 max-[640px]:border-b-0">How I work</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-ink-700 py-4 border-b border-ink-100">I believe all projects are collobarative efforts across a range of teams and disciplines, often with different goals and metrics for sucess. As such I believe communication is the core skill of a developer, and that documentation and transparency are non-optional in any well run project. To this end, I believe the quality of code and the satisfaction of the end-user are heavily shaped by the processes in place.</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-eyebrow text-ink-400 py-4 border-b border-ink-100 max-[640px]:pb-1 max-[640px]:border-b-0">Stack</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-ink-700 py-4 border-b border-ink-100 flex flex-wrap gap-1 items-start">
                <span class="font-mono text-xs rounded py-0.5 px-2 inline-block bg-paper-200 text-ink-600">Swift</span>
                <span class="font-mono text-xs rounded py-0.5 px-2 inline-block bg-paper-200 text-ink-600">SwiftUI</span>
                <span class="font-mono text-xs rounded py-0.5 px-2 inline-block bg-paper-200 text-ink-600">UIKit</span>
                <span class="font-mono text-xs rounded py-0.5 px-2 inline-block bg-paper-200 text-ink-600">Kotlin</span>
                <span class="font-mono text-xs rounded py-0.5 px-2 inline-block bg-paper-200 text-ink-600">Jetpack Compose</span>
                <span class="font-mono text-xs rounded py-0.5 px-2 inline-block bg-paper-200 text-ink-600">Java</span>
            </span>

            <span class="font-mono text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-eyebrow text-ink-400 py-4 border-b border-ink-100 max-[640px]:pb-1 max-[640px]:border-b-0">Reach me</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-ink-700 py-4 border-b border-ink-100">
                <a href="mailto:hi@ajscanlan.dev" class="text-ink-900 no-underline border-b border-ink-200 hover:text-fox-ink hover:border-fox-ink">hi@ajscanlan.dev</a>
                <span class="mx-1.5 text-ink-300">·</span>
                <a href="https://github.com/AJScanlan" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-ink-900 no-underline border-b border-ink-200 hover:text-fox-ink hover:border-fox-ink">GitHub</a>
            </span>

            <span class="font-mono text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-eyebrow text-ink-400 py-4 border-b border-ink-100 max-[640px]:pb-1 max-[640px]:border-b-0">This site</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-ink-700 py-4 border-b border-ink-100">Astro 5 · TypeScript · Tailwind · MDX · hosted on Github Pages</span>
        </div>

    </div>
</BaseLayout>
